      "content": "it's not just a \"moment\" though. it feels permanent. like the version of me that could actually face the world, and keep everyone happy, and succeed... that part of me is just gone. the shell that's left is just a mistake. how am i supposed to keep pretending to be someone who doesn't even exist anymore?",
